## How we work

**Month one** is diagnostic. I run a full technical audit, competitor analysis, and keyword mapping. You receive a prioritised roadmap — not a 60-page PDF you will never read, but a clear action plan ranked by revenue impact.

**Months two and three** focus on technical fixes and collection page optimisation. This is where the structural Shopify issues get resolved and your highest-value pages get properly optimised.

**Month four onwards** shifts to content, link building, and ongoing optimisation. I track rankings, traffic, and revenue weekly, adjusting the strategy based on what the data shows.

I work directly with your Shopify developer if you have one, or I handle the Liquid template changes myself. Either way, nothing gets implemented without your approval.

